OOC: Good bye Logo. It has been really fun RPing with you. I'll take
care of KitKat2.

::Hot Rod::

He jumped out of the shots way. The next site horrified him.
"Nooooooooooooooo!"
He ran to her lifeless body.
"That was never what I wanted. Never wanted to reprogram you, hurt you,
or anything els. I just wanted us to be together."
He held her in his arms, sobing.

::Epyon::

He lestens to the message being played.
OOC: I dont know what is being said, could someone tell me?)

::DrillBit::

He walks to the mess hall with KitKat3 and sits with Ram-Jet.
"Ok, whats this about attacking?"

::Dollon::

He ran out after DarkMouse and saw what she did.
"Well at least you are at peace."
He walks back in getting drunk on more energin.

::Demolition::

He just woundered silently with the Warmachines like always.

OOC: And now...

::KitKat2::

She took a step back from Najah, and transformed to bot mode.
